<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Candle" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Candle,</orth> a taper, a light: <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.106" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 106</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.269" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 3, 269</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.253" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 253</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.79" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 9, 79</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 5.90.79" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 90</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 5.90.79" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 90</bibl> <bibl n="shak. shr 4.5.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 5, 14</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 4.2.87" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. IV, 2, 87</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 3.3.12" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 3, 12</bibl> <emph>(bell, book and c.;</emph> see <cit><quote>book).</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.1.49" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 1, 49</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.177" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 177</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.177" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 177</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.267" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 267</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.96" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 96</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.4.237" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 4, 237</bibl>. <cit><quote>must I hold a c. to my shames?</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.6.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 6, 41</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>seek him with c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.1.6" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 1, 6</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I see no more in you than without c. may go dark to bed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.5.39" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 39</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>those gold --s fixed in heaven's air,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 21.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 21, 12</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>by these blessed --s of the night,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 5.220" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. V, 220</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>night's --s are burnt out,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 3.5.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 5, 9</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.1.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 1, 5</bibl>. -- Used as a symbol of life: <cit><quote>here burns my c. out,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.6.1" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 6, 1</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>out, out, brief c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 5.5.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 5, 23</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>